[A total of 2015 newly confirmed cases have been reported by China in the past 24 hours compared with 3062 on 9 Feb 2020 and 2478 10 Feb 2020. Perhaps there is a decreasing daily confirmation trend beginning. This brings the total number of reported confirmed cases to 44 653 cases. In addition, 97 deaths were reported in this time period, bringing the total number of reported deaths to 1113. In the past 24 hours, there have been 7 newly confirmed cases reported from Hong Kong.

A good map of China showing provinces can be found at https://www.chinadiscovery.com/china-maps/china-provincial-map.html and a HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be seen at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=6979942,155. - Mod.MPP]

